        <p>
            Where am I? Where have I been?<br />
            This section is dedicated to my <strong>adventures</strong> around the globe.<br />
            On the map you can see which countries I visited and which not.<br />
            <strong>Click</strong> on a nation to learn more about my experience there.
        </p>
